{"word":"ραίω","slug":"ραίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ραίω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to break, shiver, shatter, wreck</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>;— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ραιόμενος</el> <i>one shipwrecked</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>φάσγανον ἐρραίσθη</el> <i>was shivered</i>, <b>Il</b>.<p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to crush, destroy</i>, in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}